{"tid":1168655,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Panic 發表搭載獨特「搖柄」玩法的新型掌機「Playdate」 預定 2020 年上市","createTime":"2019-05-23T23:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:25:08.000Z","uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6532b68e10ec35ef48267a7ec25e40ff6c41c6d8","tid":1168655,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T23:37:46.000Z","msg":"原文： <a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/179926.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F6%2F179926.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=73f7d49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/179926.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國 Mac 與 iOS 應用軟體與遊戲開發發行商 Panic 5 月 23 日發表採用「搖柄（Crank）」等嶄新操作設計概念的掌上型遊戲主機「Playdate」，預定 2019 年下半開放預購，2020 年初上市，包含每週更新的第 1 季共 12 款遊戲在內的本體價格為 149 美元，折合新台幣約 4700 元。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/68/37c038734fb3ae906adf2c28f214xnw5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F68%2F37c038734fb3ae906adf2c28f214xnw5.JPG&h=52a6f288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  「Playdate」採用簡潔親和的方形平板設計與鵝黃色配色，尺寸僅 74mm &times; 76mm &times; 9mm。採用 Sharp 製作的 400 x 240 高密度高對比反射式黑白液晶螢幕。操作部分除了基本的方向鍵與 A、B 兩個按鈕之外，還在側面搭載了可收納的「搖柄」，能以轉動搖柄的方式來操作遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/47/009fb5070d98830fb572bbd47414xnb5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F47%2F009fb5070d98830fb572bbd47414xnb5.JPG&h=4699ee91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/71/ab9499b4a05d0084a31030eb3c14xnz5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F71%2Fab9499b4a05d0084a31030eb3c14xnz5.JPG&h=9b96e35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/83/7178c95ea1f6f78b43545c273414xob5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F83%2F7178c95ea1f6f78b43545c273414xob5.JPG&h=b107a05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/49/23f5427e204df725b8298a543514xnd5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F49%2F23f5427e204df725b8298a543514xnd5.JPG&h=f6c8aa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/70/ba846833baa48bb4041388d1e214xny5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F70%2Fba846833baa48bb4041388d1e214xny5.JPG&h=d76b3b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  Playdate 內建 Wi-Fi 與藍牙無線傳輸，可透過網路連線自動更新最新遊戲。將以 12 週為 1 季的週期來提供遊戲軟體。每季提供 12 款，每週一更新 1 款。目前已經確定一手打造《塊魂》系列的高橋慶太將會提供新作《克蘭金的時光旅行冒險（Crankin&rsquo;s Time Travel Adventure）》，此外還有《SpellTower》的扎克&middot;蓋格（Zach Gage）、《鐵鎚爬山》的班尼特&middot;佛迪（Bennett Foddy）以及經手過多款手機遊戲的設計師尚恩&middot;英蒙（Shaun Inman）等知名獨立遊戲創作者參與。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/72/e525b8bda355bc8e9ee1a136ff14xo05.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F72%2Fe525b8bda355bc8e9ee1a136ff14xo05.PNG&h=6b180b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  目前已公布遊戲畫面的《克蘭金的時光旅行冒險》，就是利用 Playdate 特有的搖柄來遊玩。玩家可以透過正轉與反轉搖柄來控制遊戲時間的流向，透過反覆嘗試來讓主角克蘭金順利通關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=17&amp;v=2EqQkGdZZGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D17%26v%3D2EqQkGdZZGI&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=50b42088\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=17&amp;v=2EqQkGdZZGI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=78&amp;v=CsTgVGmbCSE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D78%26v%3DCsTgVGmbCSE&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=39bbcdca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=78&amp;v=CsTgVGmbCSE</a><br />\n<br />\n原文： <a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/179926.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F6%2F179926.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=73f7d49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/179926.html</a>"},{"pid":"5a4f1926b8d899ea873de7e09dcf2e7212e85069","tid":1168655,"uid":25367,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T23:38:33.000Z","msg":"2019年重出黑白掌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a7a6d6af0f2c9c864265842ce1157982d00b16","tid":1168655,"uid":90259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T00:46:18.000Z","msg":"黑白機賣成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵Bennett Foddy就知佢地係乜都唔識"},{"pid":"e0b9485033d630db6d98e3e451cb137a7b4dfe02","tid":1168655,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"支搖柄捱唔捱到半年？"},{"pid":"8beeda9ccdeece3202eec0fa4f4fad0219817fb9","tid":1168655,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T00:49:03.000Z","msg":"2019年仲出gameboy"},{"pid":"91c41ecea83eb1c3aa7278b2a3802434f2909f17","tid":1168655,"uid":31837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"我認我蠢，我睇完個game play都唔明隻game個賣點喺邊<br />\n無論向前定向後行，個鐘都係keep住計時，個約會都係fail，咁玩嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846c631881f64d4215eb206885e40fd6935cc6fe","tid":1168655,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:07:39.000Z","msg":"伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f533a7c8a03b8e6cf6ec2fded22349d72b174225","tid":1168655,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"釣魚機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5982efc6fbebd08bedd5ce1f2507a67294db49dc","tid":1168655,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":